{"tid":656051,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"耳塞耳嗚","createTime":"2018-05-07T01:55:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T02:14:35.000Z","uid":16079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b8f1f48bc76bcece248f5c648b41c34c702d57fb","tid":656051,"uid":16079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T01:55:19.000Z","msg":"本身隻左耳經常都好痕<br />\n睇過唔同醫生照過隻左耳都話冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n醫生叫我滴d耳水 完全係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n岩岩左耳又好痕我忍唔住用錦花棒liu左一liu （我知我on9抵屌）<br />\n屌佢老母依家痕係冇痕啦 但塞撚左又少少耳嗚<br />\n係咪d耳屎塞住左？但我隻左耳自從痕以來都好少耳屎<br />\n定會唔會耳膜穿左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家2邊聽力唔平衡個人好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n人在英國 我個town的醫生差唔多個個都話我冇事<br />\n個問題好困擾 有冇巴絲救救我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba67e49593e999ff5ae7abaf2d72b9362f0f7148","tid":656051,"uid":115323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T01:58:49.000Z","msg":"再睇醫生 仲上連登問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f0e314baebb3bc2f41b03e4e14e54c678a292f","tid":656051,"uid":16079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba67e49593e999ff5ae7abaf2d72b9362f0f7148","tid":656051,"uid":115323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T01:58:49.000Z","msg":"再睇醫生 仲上連登問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T02:14:35.000Z","msg":"聽朝會睇 因為依家英國3am <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}